---
title: Ricotta and Zucchini Fritters with Olive Grove Salad
description: These unassuming zucchini fritters are an unexpected flavour revelation! Ricotta keeps these pan-fried fritters moist and fluffy, while Parmesan adds flavour complexity. Garlic aioli is just the dip you need!
